===Noun===
'''lizard''' (''plural'' '''lizards''')

# Any [[reptile]]s of the order Squamata, usually having four legs, external ear openings and [[movable]] [[eyelid]]s.
# (''colloquial'') An [[unctuous]] person.<!--was "a slimy individual"; is this a correct definition?-->
# (''colloquial'') A coward.

